<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="suggestion-n">suggestion <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /sə'dʒestʃən/    美 /sə'dʒestʃən/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 建议：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>make a</strong> useful / timely <strong>suggestion</strong>
提出有用的/及时的建议</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is so stubborn that I failed to persuade him to accept our suggestion. 
他太顽固了，我没能说服他接受我们的建议。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’d like to make some suggestions on English teaching and learning in our school.
我想就我校的英语教学提出一些建议。</p><footer>2010 江苏书面表达</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>the suggestion (is) that … (should) do:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He made the suggestion that all the political prisoners (should) be set free. 
他提议释放所有的政治犯。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The professor’s suggestion is that students should review in time after learning. 
教授的建议是学生们学完后应该及时复习。</p></div>

<h4 id="2c-u">2.<strong>[C] &amp; [U] 暗示；迹象：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There was <strong>a suggestion of</strong> anger in her face. 
她面带怒色。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— Why not buy a second-hand car first if you don’t have enough money for a new one?
— That’s a good <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (建议).  （2014 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. suggestion  </p></div>